---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---
<div id="home" class="relative min-h-[95vh] flex items-center justify-center px-6 overflow-hidden bg-[#121212] pt-20">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#121212]/70 to-[#121212]/98 z-10"></div>
    <img 
      src="https://i.ibb.co/m58jSRpT/hero-bg.jpg" 
      alt="Kilo Taxi Background" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 mix-blend-lighten z-0"
    />
  </div>
  
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[300px] md:w-[600px] h-[300px] md:h-[600px] bg-[#F5C518]/10 rounded-full blur-[130px] pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center z-10 relative">
    <div data-aos="fade-up" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-xs font-medium tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#F5C518] animate-pulse"></span>
      SMART & PREMIUM MOBILITY
    </div>

    <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 leading-[1.4] md:leading-[1.3]">
      မှန်ကန်တိကျ စိတ်ချယုံကြည် <br class="hidden sm:block"/>
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F5C518] to-[#FFD700] pt-2 inline-block">
        Kilo Taxi Service
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400" class="text-sm md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-loose">
      ခေတ်မှီနည်းပညာများနှင့် ပေါင်းစပ်ထားပြီး ဘေးကင်းစိတ်ချရမှု၊ တိကျမှုနှင့် သက်တောင့်သက်သာရှိမှုကို အပြည့်အဝပေးမည့် မြန်မာ့ပထမဆုံး Kilo-based တက္ကစီဝန်ဆောင်မှု
    </p>

    <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="#application" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-[#F5C518] text-black font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-[#FFD700] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(245,197,24,0.2)] transition-all duration-200 text-center text-sm md:text-base">
        Get Started
      </a>
      <a href="#fleet" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 text-white font-medium rounded-xl border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-200 text-center backdrop-blur-sm text-sm md:text-base">
        Our Fleet
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>